entries.title: US sec of state Blinken speaks with senior Chinese official over cancelled visit
entries.description: US secretary of state Antony Blinken has spoken with a senior Chinese official about his postponed trip to the country.

entries.title: Japanese outrage over 'sushi terrorism' sees shares plummet
entries.description: Shares in some of Japan's most popular sushi restaurants have plummeted after incidents of "sushi terrorism" were published online.

entries.title: By saying they have 'the means to respond', Putin has made a clear threat to widen war on Ukraine
entries.description: How worried should we be by Vladimir Putin's latest chilling threat of a different kind of war delivered on a key anniversary for Russians - the 80th anniversary of their victory at Stalingrad over Germany?

entries.title: Fashion designer Paco Rabanne dies aged 88
entries.description: Paco Rabanne, the Spanish-born designer, has died at the age of 88 in Portsall, Brittany.

entries.title: Chinese spy balloon heading eastwards as US sec of state Blinken cancels visit
entries.description: The US defence department has said the Chinese spy balloon is heading eastwards but poses "no physical or military threat" to civilians.

entries.title: Spy balloon over US is actually 'civilian airship' that blew off course, says China
entries.description: China has said a suspected spy balloon that has been flying over the US was in fact a "civilian airship" that had strayed into American airspace.

entries.title: Ford to return to Formula 1 in 2026
entries.description: Ford will return to Formula One from 2026, the US carmaker has said.

entries.title: UK to host summit in bid to ban Russia from 2024 Olympics
entries.description: Opposition to Russians being allowed to compete at next year's Paris Olympics is intensifying, as the UK government prepares to convene talks with more than 30 countries.

entries.title: One of UK's most wanted arrested in Morocco over Essex drive-by shooting
entries.description: A man wanted in connection with a drive-by killing in Essex has been arrested by police in Morocco.

entries.title: China 'spy' balloon: What are they? And why could they play a key role in the future of aerial reconnaissance?
entries.description: In an era of orbital satellites so advanced that they are able to make out objects half the size of cars from space, a spy balloon might seem like a bit of a relic.

entries.title: Meet 30-year-old 'miracle' Bobi - the world's oldest dog ever
entries.description: A 30-year-old dog who lives in Portugal has been named as the world's oldest by Guinness World Records.

entries.title: Tennis star Kyrgios avoids conviction after pleading guilty to assaulting ex-girlfriend
entries.description: Australian tennis star Nick Kyrgios has avoided a conviction after pleading guilty to assaulting an ex-girlfriend.

entries.title: Care centre fined after woman sent to funeral home in a body bag was found to be alive
entries.description: A US care centre has been fined 10,000 dollars (£8,185) after a funeral home discovered a woman sent to it in a body bag was still alive.
